Strength up, veins bursting.

00:13:45.674 --> 00:13:47.554
Win big, lose more.
Trades life for victory.

00:13:48.753 --> 00:13:50.593
Can only be used as a last resort.

00:13:51.993 --> 00:13:53.194
She's only alive now

00:13:53.954 --> 00:13:55.473
thanks to that cavern filled

00:13:55.473 --> 00:13:57.233
with Yuwang Meat
beneath the chasm water.

