00:15:23.336 --> 00:15:25.496
Diversity prevents creative stagnation.

00:15:25.697 --> 00:15:26.336
Right?

00:15:26.777 --> 00:15:28.697
I think it's positive. Really.

00:15:28.976 --> 00:15:30.777
Just be patient.

00:15:30.976 --> 00:15:31.616
She'll be fine.

