00:22:14.833 --> 00:22:15.593
Pick one.

00:22:15.793 --> 00:22:16.512
Pick one.

00:22:17.432 --> 00:22:19.952
I'll pick this one.

00:22:48.393 --> 00:22:49.153
Where's he?

00:22:49.633 --> 00:22:50.432
Mr. Yan?

00:22:51.192 --> 00:22:51.833
He left.

00:22:53.393 --> 00:22:54.272
Why?

00:22:55.272 --> 00:22:56.712
You don't want him to be here.

00:22:57.272 --> 00:22:59.073
I think he found it awkward
to stay here,

00:22:59.073 --> 00:22:59.992
so he left.

00:23:29.937 --> 00:23:31.416
What did Ms. Lu say?

00:23:32.785 --> 00:23:34.305
She told me to get some fresh air.

00:23:34.825 --> 00:23:36.184
Stop treating her like a child,

00:23:36.385 --> 00:23:37.704
coaxing and indulging her.

00:23:37.704 --> 00:23:38.664
That won't work.

00:23:40.752 --> 00:23:42.025
Not sure if she's comforting me

00:23:42.025 --> 00:23:43.385
or just trying a desperate mean.

00:23:44.105 --> 00:23:45.625
Ms. Lu makes a good point.

00:23:46.385 --> 00:23:47.424
Don't go back just yet.

00:23:48.385 --> 00:23:49.105
Why?

00:23:49.825 --> 00:23:51.305
The more you coax her,

00:23:51.744 --> 00:23:53.144
the less she cares for you.

00:23:53.904 --> 00:23:55.184
Keep some distance from her,

00:23:55.585 --> 00:23:57.625
and she might see your value.

00:23:57.649 --> 00:23:58.449
Exactly.

00:23:59.290 --> 00:24:00.530
To achieve something,

00:24:00.810 --> 00:24:02.010
try to go against the grain.

00:24:03.010 --> 00:24:04.369
The more you seek strength,

00:24:04.850 --> 00:24:05.969
the weaker you must appear.

00:24:06.369 --> 00:24:07.449
The more you desire,

00:24:07.810 --> 00:24:08.969
the more you must let go.

00:24:09.610 --> 00:24:10.409
The same to her.

00:24:11.250 --> 00:24:12.409
The harder she recalls,

00:24:13.050 --> 00:24:14.169
the more she'll forget.

00:24:16.449 --> 00:24:18.530
Learn this wisdom at the archery range?

00:24:21.530 --> 00:24:23.250
If you focus too hard on the bullseye,

00:24:23.689 --> 00:24:25.050
your form will fall apart.

00:24:25.689 --> 00:24:26.770
Score drops.

00:24:27.209 --> 00:24:27.889
Then,

00:24:29.169 --> 00:24:30.250
what should I do?

00:24:31.090 --> 00:24:32.129
To draw the bow,

00:24:32.490 --> 00:24:34.129
not only arm strength alone needed,

00:24:34.729 --> 00:24:35.810
but also relaxation.

00:24:36.770 --> 00:24:38.209
Engage every muscle in your body

00:24:38.409 --> 00:24:39.330
to draw the bow fully.

00:24:40.010 --> 00:24:41.929
Focus on perfecting every single detail.

00:24:42.209 --> 00:24:43.369
Don't go after the outcome.

00:24:44.944 --> 00:24:46.449
(This applies to you and Nie Jiuluo.)

00:24:47.010 --> 00:24:49.649
(Treasure her and you at the moment.)

00:24:50.409 --> 00:24:51.610
(Let the fate work.)

00:25:41.664 --> 00:25:43.248
(Joy Comes Upon, Moving Forward)

00:26:51.409 --> 00:26:52.330
Wherever you go,

00:26:52.330 --> 00:26:53.609
you need my permission first.

00:26:56.090 --> 00:26:56.850
Okay.

00:26:57.290 --> 00:26:58.649
But solving things with words,

00:26:58.649 --> 00:26:59.409
not fists.

00:26:59.490 --> 00:27:00.129
Okay.

00:27:01.169 --> 00:27:02.730
But it depends on the situations.

00:27:02.929 --> 00:27:03.850
Extreme ones excluded.

00:27:05.689 --> 00:27:06.290
Okay.

00:27:08.409 --> 00:27:10.570
Chat with me
for at least fifteen minutes every day.

00:27:12.889 --> 00:27:13.730
Okay.

00:27:14.409 --> 00:27:15.770
But it depends on the topics.

00:27:15.969 --> 00:27:17.169
The ones I hate excluded.

00:27:17.330 --> 00:27:17.850
Okay.

00:27:17.850 --> 00:27:19.369
Read five stars every day.

00:27:19.969 --> 00:27:20.770
Let's work together

00:27:20.770 --> 00:27:22.129
to regain your memory.

00:27:22.330 --> 00:27:23.449
Okay.

00:27:24.209 --> 00:27:25.689
But I'll only open and read them.

00:27:25.969 --> 00:27:27.129
I won't fold them back.

00:27:27.209 --> 00:27:27.770
Okay.

00:27:31.490 --> 00:27:32.929
Travel with me.

00:27:34.530 --> 00:27:35.169
Short trips.

00:27:35.290 --> 00:27:36.090
Three days maximum.

00:27:41.570 --> 00:27:42.369
Okay.

00:27:43.010 --> 00:27:43.689
Really?

00:27:44.689 --> 00:27:45.449
Fine, forget it.

00:27:45.689 --> 00:27:46.969
No, we're definitely going.

00:27:47.010 --> 00:27:47.889
It's settled then.

00:28:05.850 --> 00:28:06.929
This is tacky and ugly.

00:28:06.929 --> 00:28:08.129
Why are you hanging it here?

00:28:08.449 --> 00:28:09.369
Don't touch it.

00:28:09.530 --> 00:28:11.409
It's my treasure.

00:28:16.969 --> 00:28:17.770
Well,

00:28:18.689 --> 00:28:19.810
how many minutes left today?

00:28:21.169 --> 00:28:22.369
I set an alarm.

00:28:22.369 --> 00:28:23.649
It'll ring when time's up.

00:28:23.969 --> 00:28:25.689
It's okay to end the conversation now.

00:28:25.850 --> 00:28:26.689
No way.

00:28:26.689 --> 00:28:27.929
We agreed on fifteen minutes.

00:28:28.129 --> 00:28:28.850
Make them count.

00:28:30.929 --> 00:28:33.169
Well, you drove me
up the mountain overnight,

00:28:33.530 --> 00:28:35.169
made a natural fire for me at the peak,

00:28:35.169 --> 00:28:36.010
and saved my life.

00:28:36.010 --> 00:28:37.090
You remember that, right?

00:28:38.409 --> 00:28:39.570
I caught your lie.

00:28:40.290 --> 00:28:42.250
Didn't you say I saved you in the mine?

00:28:42.250 --> 00:28:43.649
Why mention the natural fire now?

00:28:43.850 --> 00:28:45.170
You saved me twice.

00:28:45.170 --> 00:28:46.490
First time with the natural fire.

00:28:46.490 --> 00:28:47.730
Second time in the mine.

00:28:48.169 --> 00:28:48.929
As a grown man,

00:28:48.929 --> 00:28:50.369
you need me to save you twice?

00:28:51.152 --> 00:28:52.225
I've saved you too.

00:28:52.225 --> 00:28:53.584
When you got hurt at the shipyard,

00:28:53.584 --> 00:28:55.010
I showed up in time.

00:28:55.010 --> 00:28:55.649
That was...

00:29:03.389 --> 00:29:03.889
Fine.

00:29:03.889 --> 00:29:06.169
Save it for next time.

00:29:23.889 --> 00:29:24.449
Here.

00:29:39.770 --> 00:29:40.889
What? What do you need?

00:29:48.010 --> 00:29:50.250
Have I had this noodle before?

00:29:50.889 --> 00:29:52.369
Yes, you have.

00:29:53.409 --> 00:29:54.810
When you went rescue Mr. Crip,

00:29:54.810 --> 00:29:55.889
I was hurt by Locust.

00:29:55.889 --> 00:29:57.290
And you made a natural fire for me.

00:29:58.129 --> 00:29:59.250
Later, Jiang got captured

00:29:59.250 --> 00:30:00.449
and you came to me. Remember?

00:30:05.929 --> 00:30:06.689
Jiang?

00:30:06.929 --> 00:30:07.570
Yes.

00:30:11.290 --> 00:30:12.050
Mad Blade.

00:30:21.850 --> 00:30:22.610
Jiang.

00:30:28.945 --> 00:30:30.425
It's okay, Luo.

00:30:32.945 --> 00:30:33.625
It's okay.

00:30:35.465 --> 00:30:36.344
Luo.

00:30:37.704 --> 00:30:38.224
Luo...

00:31:00.144 --> 00:31:00.704
Asleep?

00:31:48.744 --> 00:31:51.304
(Ms. Lu is excellent.
I've decided to keep her.)

00:31:56.224 --> 00:32:00.105
(The osmanthus tree is blooming.
We'll get to eat osmanthus sauce.)

00:32:05.065 --> 00:32:06.905
(Gave Yan Tuo a haircut.)

00:32:07.144 --> 00:32:10.505
(He should recover soon. Keep it up!)

00:32:19.465 --> 00:32:22.224
(Yan Tuo, Lin Ling,
Ms. Lu, Mr. Changxi.)

00:32:22.385 --> 00:32:25.344
(We had hot pot together as family.)

00:32:25.585 --> 00:32:27.465
(And we saw a meteor shower.)

00:32:36.864 --> 00:32:37.704
Family?

00:32:47.573 --> 00:32:48.293
No way.

00:32:48.573 --> 00:32:49.533
You're making a mess.

00:32:49.533 --> 00:32:50.172
You...

00:32:50.293 --> 00:32:51.652
Others can't get any then.

00:32:54.452 --> 00:32:55.652
You've put your whole face in.

00:32:56.952 --> 00:32:57.452
Hold on.

00:32:57.452 --> 00:32:58.452
Hold on.

00:33:01.452 --> 00:33:02.253
Wait.

00:33:08.732 --> 00:33:09.452
Hello.

00:33:10.492 --> 00:33:11.293
Where are you?

00:33:12.732 --> 00:33:14.932
I-I'm out meeting a client.

00:33:15.373 --> 00:33:16.293
Come back now.

00:33:19.813 --> 00:33:21.452
Today? But I...

00:33:22.373 --> 00:33:23.492
I haven't finished my work.

00:33:23.492 --> 00:33:24.492
How about tomorrow?

00:33:25.333 --> 00:33:26.652
Is it urgent?

00:33:28.813 --> 00:33:29.932
I'll try my best

00:33:30.013 --> 00:33:31.412
to get back early.

00:33:31.732 --> 00:33:32.452
How early?

00:33:35.492 --> 00:33:36.773
If I can go back today,

00:33:36.773 --> 00:33:38.333
can we discuss something?

00:33:38.892 --> 00:33:39.853
Talk when you're back.

00:33:39.853 --> 00:33:41.462
Wait, let's say...

00:33:42.201 --> 00:33:42.864
Hello.

00:33:43.536 --> 00:33:44.437
Hello?

00:33:47.088 --> 00:33:54.800
♪Farewell to the old times,
and scenes fade away one by one♪